reviewText: I really would have enjoyed this movie it's one of my favorite movies of all times but unfortunately it never arrived after numerous postponements and now I can't even get a hold of them for a refund what a pity
One of the greatest movies ever made, this film still seems fresh and new even though it was released way back in 1975.

As a current "inmate" in several Nursing/ Rehab Facilities in Illinois over the past 4-5 years, I can whole-heartedly identify with "McMurphy"; as I am MENSA Certified fighting off these facility's effort(s) to "dummy me down".
Love watching this over and over.
